							<span class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed text-[10px] uppercase font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Gift Pack</span>
						</div>
						<div class="p-6">
							<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-1">Oleh-Oleh Premium</h3>
							<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4">Elegant packaging for your special ones.</p>
							<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
